WITH MovieStats AS (
    SELECT 
        t.id AS movie_id,
        t.title,
        t.production_year,
        COUNT(ci.person_id) AS cast_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT ak.name, ', ') AS actor_names,
        COUNT(DISTINCT mk.keyword_id) AS keyword_count
    FROM 
        title t
    JOIN 
        complete_cast cc ON t.id = cc.movie_id
    JOIN 
        cast_info ci ON cc.subject_id = ci.id
    JOIN 
        aka_name ak ON ci.person_id = ak.person_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        movie_keyword mk ON t.id = mk.movie_id
    GROUP BY 
        t.id, t.title, t.production_year
),
CompanyStats AS (
    SELECT 
        mc.movie_id,
        COUNT(DISTINCT c.name) AS company_count,
        STRING_AGG(DISTINCT c.name, ', ') AS company_names
    FROM 
        movie_companies mc
    JOIN 
        company_name c ON mc.company_id = c.id
    GROUP BY 
        mc.movie_id
)
SELECT 
    ms.movie_id,
    ms.title,
    ms.production_year,
    ms.cast_count,
    ms.actor_names,
    ms.keyword_count,
    cs.company_count,
    cs.company_names
FROM 
    MovieStats ms
LEFT JOIN 
    CompanyStats cs ON ms.movie_id = cs.movie_id
WHERE 
    ms.production_year >= 2000
ORDER BY 
    ms.production_year DESC, ms.cast_count DESC, cs.company_count DESC

SELECT COALESCE("t2"."MOVIE_ID", "t2"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t2"."TITLE", "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t2"."CAST_COUNT", "t2"."ACTOR_NAMES", "t2"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "t4"."COMPANY_COUNT", "t4"."COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT MIN("title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "title"."title" AS "TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(*) AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES", COUNT(DISTINCT "s1"."keyword_id") AS "KEYWORD_COUNT"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "title"."id" = "s1"."movie_id"
GROUP BY "title"."id", "title"."title", "title"."production_year") AS "t2"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "movie_companies"."movie_id" AS "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "company_name"."name") AS "COMPANY_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM "movie_companies"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
GROUP BY "movie_companies"."movie_id") AS "t4" ON "t2"."MOVIE_ID" = "t4"."MOVIE_ID"
WHERE "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000
ORDER BY "t2"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t2"."CAST_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."COMPANY_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST

SELECT COALESCE("movie_companies"."movie_id", "movie_companies"."movie_id") AS "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "company_name"."name") AS "COMPANY_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "company_name"."name", ', ') AS "COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM "movie_companies"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"
GROUP BY "movie_companies"."movie_id"

SELECT COALESCE("t4"."MOVIE_ID", "t4"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t4"."TITLE", "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t4"."CAST_COUNT", "t4"."ACTOR_NAMES", "t4"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "s1"."COMPANY_COUNT", "s1"."COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT MIN("title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "title"."title" AS "TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(*) AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES", COUNT(DISTINCT "movie_keyword"."keyword_id") AS "KEYWORD_COUNT"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
GROUP BY "title"."id", "title"."title", "title"."production_year") AS "t4"
LEFT JOIN "s1" ON "t4"."MOVIE_ID" = "s1"."MOVIE_ID"
WHERE "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000
ORDER BY "t4"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."CAST_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "s1"."COMPANY_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST

SELECT COALESCE("movie_companies"."movie_id", "movie_companies"."movie_id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "company_name"."name", ', ' AS "FD_COL_2"
FROM "movie_companies"
INNER JOIN "company_name" ON "movie_companies"."company_id" = "company_name"."id"

SELECT COALESCE("t3"."MOVIE_ID", "t3"."MOVIE_ID") AS "MOVIE_ID", "t3"."TITLE", "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR", "t3"."CAST_COUNT", "t3"."ACTOR_NAMES", "t3"."KEYWORD_COUNT", "t4"."COMPANY_COUNT", "t4"."COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM (SELECT MIN("title"."id") AS "MOVIE_ID", "title"."title" AS "TITLE", "title"."production_year" AS "PRODUCTION_YEAR", COUNT(*) AS "CAST_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "aka_name"."name", ', ') AS "ACTOR_NAMES", COUNT(DISTINCT "movie_keyword"."keyword_id") AS "KEYWORD_COUNT"
FROM "title"
INNER JOIN "complete_cast" ON "title"."id" = "complete_cast"."movie_id"
INNER JOIN "cast_info" ON "complete_cast"."subject_id" = "cast_info"."id"
INNER JOIN "aka_name" ON "cast_info"."person_id" = "aka_name"."person_id"
LEFT JOIN "movie_keyword" ON "title"."id" = "movie_keyword"."movie_id"
GROUP BY "title"."id", "title"."title", "title"."production_year") AS "t3"
LEFT JOIN (SELECT "MOVIE_ID", COUNT(DISTINCT "name") AS "COMPANY_COUNT", LISTAGG(DISTINCT "name", "FD_COL_2") AS "COMPANY_NAMES"
FROM "s1"
GROUP BY "MOVIE_ID") AS "t4" ON "t3"."MOVIE_ID" = "t4"."MOVIE_ID"
WHERE "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" >= 2000
ORDER BY "t3"."PRODUCTION_YEAR" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t3"."CAST_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST, "t4"."COMPANY_COUNT" DESC NULLS FIRST
